---
title: Rust所有权转移流程
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant Main as main()
    participant S as s: String
    participant T as t: String
    participant Heap as 堆内存
    participant Drop as Drop Trait
    
    Main->>Heap: 分配内存
    Heap-->>S: 创建String::from("hello")
    Note over S: s拥有堆内存所有权<br/>s = ptr + len + capacity
    
    Main->>S: let t = s
    Note over S: 所有权转移发生<br/>Move语义
    
    S->>T: 转移所有权<br/>ptr, len, capacity
    Note over S: s变为未初始化状态<br/>s不可用
    Note over T: t获得所有权<br/>t可用
    
    Main->>T: println!("{}", t)
    Note over T: t正常使用
    
    alt 尝试使用s
        Main->>S: println!("{}", s)
        Note over S: ❌ 编译错误<br/>value borrowed here after move
    end
    
    Main->>T: drop(t) / 作用域结束
    T->>Drop: 调用Drop trait
    Drop->>Heap: 释放堆内存
    Note over Heap: 内存安全释放<br/>无内存泄漏
    
    %% Copy类型对比
    Note right of Main: Copy类型对比
    Main->>Main: let x = 5i32
    Main->>Main: let y = x
    Note over Main: x被复制(Copy)<br/>x和y都可用
    Main->>Main: println!("x={}, y={}", x, y)
    Note over Main: ✅ 编译通过
